{"questionId":"9990","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"M = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;{ - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>M</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>, where&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a \\in \\mathbb{Z}\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">Z</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Using this value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>, find <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{M^{ - 1}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>M</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>−</mo>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and <strong>hence </strong>solve the system of equations:</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:180px;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" - x + 2y =&nbsp; - 3\">\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:180px;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2x - y = 3\">\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  